text: Eunidia meleagris is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1926. It is known from Kenya, Ethiopia, and Somalia.BioLib.cz - Eunidia meleagris. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1926
